::Aerotaur::
    "Eh?  Yawn.  That felt good.  I'll be fine I have a bit of energy to 
spare.  I need so much energy because of my shall we say interesting 
physiology.  The changing forms takes a lot of energy because my transforming 
protocols are a bit haywire.  But the extra energy comes in handy sometimes 
so I think I like the way I am."  He looks around and sees Gramps holding the 
frog.  "So you're choosing your forms now good.  Our group is getting quite 
large isn't it Windlord.  Too many more people join us and we'll need to come 
up with a name for it."
